{"tid":2418903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國與台灣駐世貿官員會面  深化美台關係","createTime":"2021-02-23T03:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T05:27:38.000Z","uid":227801,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"72c18cf96c6261d5dbe2b6d39265ca05e20d5252","tid":2418903,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=425001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425001&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=dc3e4fca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425001&h=8d225e92\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=425001</a><br />\n6分鐘前&nbsp;<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國與台灣駐世界貿易組織的官員在日內瓦會面。<br />\n<br />\n中央社報道，美國駐世貿代表團臨時代辦比斯比，本月11日應邀到台灣駐世貿代表團辦公室，與台方代表羅昌發會面。雙方就世貿改革和美國拜登政府的展望等議題交換意見，承諾未來就共同關注的議題加強合作、持續深化美台關係及共同捍衛多邊經貿體系。<br />\n<br />\n美國前任特朗普政府解除對台交往限制，拜登政府上台後，美台官員持續有會面，對上一次是本月10日，台北駐美代表蕭美琴會見美國署理助理國務卿金成。"},{"pid":"48e6cb6594fb955449d4c5384d61230468057a99","tid":2418903,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"支支好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14億人繼續返工抗議，唔肯一齊衝過台海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5748c8ae3f9f61e11f833d5b459b8f5736a7ba7","tid":2418903,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"TSM：我準備好了"},{"pid":"95a9ede7f20f7c1b93ed6dcdb7eb319f43a81508","tid":2418903,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"我登硬起來"},{"pid":"791dd5b52a91221e5112cd8bc586962b0b56293a","tid":2418903,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23